b0 c\u00f3 s\u1eb5n do ch\u00ednh TDC ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n t\u1eeb tr\u01b0\u1edbc.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">T\u1ed5ng quan d\u1ef1 \u00e1n Ecolux City \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng v\u00e0 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n d\u1ef1a tr\u00ean kinh nghi\u1ec7m c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 ti\u00eau chu\u1ea9n v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c khu \u0111\u00f4 th\u1ecb th\u00f4ng minh, hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i. C\u00e1c ti\u1ec7n \u00edch n\u1ed9i khu c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 k\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u01b0:<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>1. H\u1ea1 t\u1ea7ng n\u1ed9i khu ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">To\u00e0n b\u1ed9 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng n\u1ed9i b\u1ed9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ea3i nh\u1ef1a, c\u00f3 v\u1ec9a h\u00e8 l\u00e1t g\u1ea1ch v\u00e0 c\u00e2y xanh b\u00f3ng m\u00e1t \u2013 t\u1ea1o kh\u00f4ng gian \u0111i b\u1ed9 an to\u00e0n, tho\u00e1ng \u0111\u00e3ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">H\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng \u0111i\u1ec7n n\u01b0\u1edbc \u00e2m, \u0111\u1ed3ng b\u1ed9 v\u00e0 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng ngay sau khi nh\u1eadn nh\u00e0.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1685\" src=\"https:\/\/ecoluxcity.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/07\/DJI_0927-scaled.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"2560\" height=\"1707\" srcset=\"https:\/\/ecoluxcity.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/07\/DJI_0927-scaled.jpg 2560w, https:\/\/ecoluxcity.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/07\/DJI_0927-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/ecoluxcity.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/07\/DJI_0927-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/ecoluxcity.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/07\/DJI_0927-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/ecoluxcity.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/07\/DJI_0927-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/ecoluxcity.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/07\/DJI_0927-2048x1365.jpg 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2560px) 100vw, 2560px\" \/><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><em>Ecolux City s\u1edf h\u1eefu l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf h\u1ea1 t\u1ea7ng hi\u1ec7n h\u1eefu v\u00e0 ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng kinh doanh, sinh l\u1ee3i ngay<\/em><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>2. M\u1eb7t b\u1eb1ng \u0111a n\u0103ng \u2013 nh\u00e0 ph\u1ed1 v\u00e0 shophouse <\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">119 c\u0103n nh\u00e0 ph\u1ed1 cao 2\u20133 t\u1ea7ng, \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed 2\u20133 m\u1eb7t ti\u1ec1n \u2013 t\u1ed1i \u01b0u cho c\u1ea3 vi\u1ec7c an c\u01b0 v\u00e0 kinh doanh nh\u01b0 cafe, v\u0103n ph\u00f2ng nh\u1ecf, showroom<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf m\u1eadt \u0111\u1ed9 th\u1ea5p (44,2%) gi\u00fap kh\u00f4ng gian n\u1ed9i b\u1ed9 tho\u00e1ng \u0111\u00e3ng v\u00e0 th\u00e2n thi\u1ec7n v\u1edbi m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng<\/span><\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1683\" src=\"https:\/\/ecoluxcity.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/07\/2_11.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"3840\" height=\"2160\" srcset=\"https:\/\/ecoluxcity.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/07\/2_11.png 3840w, https:\/\/ecoluxcity.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/07\/2_11-300x169.png 300w, https:\/\/ecoluxcity.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/07\/2_11-1024x576.png 1024w, https:\/\/ecoluxcity.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/07\/2_11-768x432.png 768w, https:\/\/ecoluxcity.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/07\/2_11-1536x864.png 1536w, https:\/\/ecoluxcity.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/07\/2_11-2048x1152.png 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 3840px) 100vw, 3840px\" \/><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><em>Ph\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh m\u1eb7t b\u1eb1ng \u0111a n\u0103ng &#8211; nh\u00e0 ph\u1ed1<\/em><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>3. Kh\u00f4ng gian xanh v\u00e0 c\u1ea3nh quan<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">C\u00f4ng vi\u00ean n\u1ed9i khu t\u00edch h\u1ee3p c\u1ea3nh quan v\u1edbi c\u00e2y xanh, l\u1ed1i \u0111i b\u1ed9 \u2013 t\u1ea1o c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c th\u01b0 gi\u00e3n, g\u1ea7n g\u0169i thi\u00ean nhi\u00ean.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">C\u00e1c kho\u1ea3ng xanh ven \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng, t\u1ea1o s\u1ef1 k\u1ebft n\u1ed1i gi\u1eefa c\u00e1c kh\u00f4ng gian c\u00f4ng c\u1ed9ng v\u00e0 nh\u00e0 \u1edf, n\u00e2ng cao ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng s\u1ed1ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><strong>4. Khu ti\u1ec7n \u00edch \u0111a ch\u1ee9c n\u0103ng<\/strong><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf ch\u1ed7 \u0111\u1ec3 xe r\u1ed9ng r\u00e3i ngay trong khu\u00f4n vi\u00ean, thu\u1eadn ti\u1ec7n cho c\u01b0 d\u00e2n v\u00e0 kh\u00e1ch thu\u00ea<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Khu mua s\u1eafm, shophouse tr\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ec1u trong d\u1ef1 \u00e1n \u2013 d\u1ec5 ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn, ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 nhu c\u1ea7u h\u00e0ng ng\u00e0y nh\u01b0 cafe, ti\u1ec7m thu\u1ed1c, c\u1eeda h\u00e0ng ti\u1ec7n l\u1ee3i, v\u0103n ph\u00f2ng d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 nh\u1ecf\u2026<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">Khu sinh ho\u1ea1t c\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ed3ng (community house) \u2013 th\u00edch h\u1ee3p t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c s\u1ef1 ki\u1ec7n c\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ed3ng nh\u01b0 h\u1ed9i h\u00e8, workshop, giao l\u01b0u c\u01b0 d\u00e2n.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1682\" src=\"https:\/\/ecoluxcity.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/07\